## Architecture Overview

### Package Layout

```
img-settings/
├── lib/                  # Pure domain logic — no GUI, no CLI coupling
│   └── watermark.go      # EXIF reading, image decoding, watermark rendering, file helpers
├── gui/                  # Fyne GUI application (CGO required)
│   ├── main.go           # App entry point, window setup, drop handler
│   ├── dropzone.go       # Drag-and-drop zone component
│   ├── processor.go      # Bridges lib.ProcessFile to GUI job results
│   ├── results.go        # Results view (progress bar + file list)
│   ├── toolbar.go        # Settings bar (opacity, output dir, recurse toggle)
│   ├── picker.go         # File/folder picker (fallback for no-DnD environments)
│   ├── theme.go          # Custom Apple-inspired Fyne theme
│   ├── util.go           # GUI utilities (path helpers, etc.)
│   ├── demo.go           # Demo mode (build tag: demo)
│   ├── demo_stub.go      # No-op stub (default build)
│   └── assets/           # Embedded assets (AppIcon.png)
├── cli/
│   └── main.go           # CLI entry point, flag parsing, parallel processing
├── .github/
│   ├── workflows/
│   │   ├── ci.yml        # go vet + build checks on every push/PR
│   │   └── release.yml   # Cross-platform binary release via semantic-release
│   └── dependabot.yml
├── docs/                 # User-facing documentation (English + Spanish)
├── scripts/              # Screenshot and sample generation utilities
├── Makefile              # Build targets
├── go.mod / go.sum
└── .releaserc.json       # Semantic-release configuration
```

### Dependency Flow

```
cli/main.go ──────────────┐
                           ▼
                      lib/watermark.go   ← pure logic, zero GUI imports
                           ▲
gui/processor.go ─────────┘
gui/*.go  ─────────────────→  fyne.io/fyne/v2  (GUI layer only)
```

**Rule**: `lib/` must never import `gui/` or `cli/`. `gui/` and `cli/` may import `lib/`. This ensures the core logic can be tested without a display server.

